        "Title": "Contract Addendum  I  v.2 : Bitter Fruit",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN_NIGHT",
        "PublicId": "104492076292",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/_scene_mamba.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository c823beec-3d73-47b6-87d9-076c384c4662).Image",
        "Description": "Agent 47,\r\rClearly, Abiatti and his partners have gained a great deal more from the deal we struck than the ICA. Mulo, Francesco, and even Bravuomo have risen to great wealth in no time at all.\r\rToday, our  client has agreed to tack his contract onto the end of the one you executed on Targets DeSantis and Caruso, in exchange for a price reduction and an assurance that the highest standards of clandestine operations are followed.\r\rGood luck\r\r[This is hard mode. The other version is easier. -OrS]",
